Package msp.simulator.dynamic.forces

Class Forces

  • java.lang.Object
    • msp.simulator.dynamic.forces.Forces

  • public class Forces
extends java.lang.Object
    Top class to represents all of the linear forces in the simulation. This class is responsible to build all of its sub-classes and to provide a set of tools and methods to access and maintain them.
    Author:
    Florian CHAUBEYRE
